    L = [0] * n
    R = [0] * n

    R[n - 1] = 0
    i = 1
    j = n - 2
    while i < n and j >= 0:
        if string[i] == string[j]:
            L[i] = L[i - 1] + 1
            R[j] = R[j + 1] + 1
            i += 1
            j -= 1
        else:
            L[i] = 0
            R[j] = 0
            i += 1
            j -= 1
    max_len = max(max(L), max(R))
    palindrome = string[:max_len]
    return palindrome + string[max_len:][::-1]

            return [smallest_even, smallest_even_index]
